name: Fanzine Series "Sunday" on Kolase Seminggu Project
description:
"Kolase Seminggu" is an Art Project that aims to visualize all the different circumstances and condition that occur in the days; Sunday - Monday.

Because the Collage Art by me is a form of the Art of Seizing and sticking, as does the feeling that is attached to every circumstance and seized by every condition. Best nice experience.
